 Check your web pages
Use one (or both) of these free validation services on the web to
        check that your pages are valid html, html2 or html3.
UniPress Weblint. 
            (2k file size limit)
	WEBTECHS
	     HTML Validation Service.  With this service you can also check for
	     compliance with Mozilla, Microsoft IE and HotJava. (No file size limit)
